*Kiša* je padala ceo dan. (It was raining all day.)

Svi su se utrkivali da pređu cestu pre nego što počne *kiša*. (Everyone was racing to cross the street before the rain started.)

Kiša iznenada prestade da pada. (The rain suddenly stopped falling.)

*Kiše* je bilo mnogo u proteklim mesecima. (There was a lot of rain in the past months.)

Kiša je nagnala ljude da se sklone u kuće. (The rain forced people to take shelter in their homes.)